      "message": "I avoided testutils.TestDataDir() because I would like this package to not depend on testutils (it feels cleaner that way). I\u0027m looking at repo_root and I\u0027m not sure it is platform independent as written.\n\nI don\u0027t quite understand what is and is not amenable to Bazel. Isn\u0027t the change https://skia-review.googlesource.com/c/buildbot/+/355498/11/golden/go/sql/datakitchensink/BUILD.bazel enough to make it work?",
